description: Lists the Amazon QuickSight groups that an Amazon QuickSight user is a member of.

parameters.name: UserName
parameters.description: The Amazon QuickSight user name that you want to list group memberships for.

parameters.name: AwsAccountId
parameters.description: The Amazon Web Services account ID that the user is in. Currently, you use the ID for the Amazon Web Services account that contains your Amazon QuickSight account.

parameters.name: Namespace
parameters.description: The namespace. Currently, you should set this to default.

nested_items.name: GroupList
nested_items.description: The list of groups the user is a member of.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for the group.

nested_items.name: PrincipalId
nested_items.description: The principal ID of the group.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: A pagination token that can be used in a subsequent request.

nested_items.name: RequestId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services request ID for this operation.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The HTTP status of the request.
